    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Mouse Practice For Kids》帮助小孩子通过点击屏幕上出现的彩色水果来学习如何使用电脑鼠标。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214720/extras/1a9cb50f4968b4ea82f2d149ed930c3a.avif?t=1760087535\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214720/extras_big/1a9cb50f4968b4ea82f2d149ed930c3a.avif?t=1760087535 width=800 height=118 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >伴随着欢快的音乐和奖励音效，《Mouse Practice for Kids》在提升精细运动技能的同时，带来愉快的体验。非常适合那些为孩子寻找有趣且具教育意义的活动的家长们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214720/extras/deecb49739971f3c4f18f34a11dfbc7f.webp?t=1760087535\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214720/extras/deecb49739971f3c4f18f34a11dfbc7f.poster.avif?t=1760087535\" class=\"bb_img\" width=300 height=300 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特点：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>教育目的：</strong> 帮助孩子们学习如何使用鼠标。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>简单游戏：</strong> 点击屏幕上出现的五颜六色的水果和蔬菜。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>家长控制计时器：</strong> 设定游戏时间限制；时间到了游戏将自动关闭。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>难度逐渐增加：</strong> 随着关卡进展，鼠标光标变小，同时水果移动并变小，增加了挑战性。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>愉快反馈：</strong> 通过有趣的音乐和音效奖励游戏进展。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的主要特色是一个心理小技巧，开始时鼠标指针和水果都很大，鼓励孩子们专注于移动鼠标并点击水果。随着关卡的进展，指针和水果会逐渐变小，直到鼠标指针达到正常的PC尺寸。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214720/extras/2049c3ac21ec9a7d140e829f71e2ff34.poster.avif?t=1760087535\" width=616 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214720/extras/2049c3ac21ec9a7d140e829f71e2ff34.webm?t=1760087535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214720/extras/2049c3ac21ec9a7d140e829f71e2ff34.mp4?t=1760087535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
